{"tid":2160409,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"記錄反送中 日導演再奪大獎","createTime":"2020-08-17T02:39:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-17T04:45:29.000Z","uid":25558,"like":32,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"9b1752a217c590fe194ee1a8b4009f33e46519be","tid":2160409,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T02:39:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200817/XKGVBDGQSBE6JEARDGIE76MUVA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200817%2FXKGVBDGQSBE6JEARDGIE76MUVA%2F&d=F9sYfJh4wRYjdPScc1OpRnqIiw1YZhwEtH0I4AgSOk0%3D&h=49f24742\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200817%2FXKGVBDGQSBE6JEARDGIE76MUVA%2F&h=f5957d70\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200817/XKGVBDGQSBE6JEARDGIE76MUVA/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n記錄反送中 日導演再奪大獎<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Qu5QT5OwZo8czxC3mczuBzQzRPU=/1772x1772/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/3OLDKB3I7NCMLOBKGEATNW6HQI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FQu5QT5OwZo8czxC3mczuBzQzRPU%3D%2F1772x1772%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F3OLDKB3I7NCMLOBKGEATNW6HQI.jpg&h=ad81da62&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n堀井威久麿<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】日本電影導演堀井威久麿（Ikuma Horii）去年來港，拍攝反送中運動紀錄片《香港画/Montage of Hong Kong》，作品繼早前獲得日本大阪門真國際電影節優秀賞後，再於同一電影節獲頒紀錄片最高榮譽的「最優秀賞」。他接受《蘋果》訪問時承認港版國安法令他感到擔憂，但仍希望將香港年輕人的抗爭力量傳遞給日本人。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：英國防部煞停培訓港警  謝振中首當其衝 與國際脫軌<br />\n<br />\n《香港画》上周四至六在當地電影節會場放映，亦同步在網上放映。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n冀傳遞抗爭力量予日本人<br />\n<br />\n堀井威久麿接受本報訪問表示，去年來港原為工作，並非為拍攝反送中運動，但因為在旺角目睹一次示威，見證香港年輕人冒生命危險戰鬥，「我一生從未如此深刻地動過，我想通過電影將其傳達給日本的年輕人」。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：美媒：港人值得全球支持<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/sypm3_QFzgrBizftkVWGs5DiMls=/1902x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/KYNYKX3HSVDHVNUQL3GIWRA5WM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fsypm3_QFzgrBizftkVWGs5DiMls%3D%2F1902x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FKYNYKX3HSVDHVNUQL3GIWRA5WM.jpg&h=0c68263c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■紀錄片拍低警察揮棍毆打示威者情況。《香港画》片段截圖<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/ug_HeamAje8leBQv1BIr1jp2PdQ=/1916x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/MIDFSUNFNFGCVGUNR3ZOBTL22E.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fug_HeamAje8leBQv1BIr1jp2PdQ%3D%2F1916x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FMIDFSUNFNFGCVGUNR3ZOBTL22E.jpg&h=6d7ada05&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■堀井去年三度來港，記錄香港年輕人冒生命危險爭取民主自由。<br />\n<br />\n紀錄片訪問了多位香港人，堀井威久麿不擅長說英語，亦完全不會廣東話，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n港版國安法下，外國記者與。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n雖然如此，他依然致力在日本推廣其紀錄片，。。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"d52a9575c5341dedabab3134c4892727e4630301","tid":2160409,"uid":242903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T02:48:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3adb19ea20e32a20ab1401afebe38b096923e18c","tid":2160409,"uid":126305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T02:52:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff6eaa26a0834d3a708229566008d31b82276213","tid":2160409,"uid":67292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T03:02:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e99f7076dffabc350c46010c5577401aac3e0aa6","tid":2160409,"uid":325840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedB